Package org.apache.juneau.html

Class HtmlClassMeta

java.lang.Object
org.apache.juneau.ExtendedMeta
org.apache.juneau.ExtendedClassMeta
org.apache.juneau.html.HtmlClassMeta
public class HtmlClassMeta extends ExtendedClassMeta
Metadata on classes specific to the HTML serializers and parsers pulled from the @Html annotation on the class.
